This Rmd file shows a running example of how to use the dataset `Ctrip_data` that we include in our package `BinaryClassifieR`.

```{r}
library(BinaryClassifieR)

data(Ctrip_data)
Ctrip_data$label
head(Ctrip_data$consuming_capacity)
head(Ctrip_data$cancelrate)
```
